		<title>寵物食品心佔率大揭密：誰是飼主們心中的TOP1品牌？</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/19/%e5%af%b5%e7%89%a9%e9%a3%9f%e5%93%81%e5%bf%83%e4%bd%94%e7%8e%87%e5%a4%a7%e6%8f%ad%e5%af%86%ef%bc%9a%e8%aa%b0%e6%98%af%e9%a3%bc%e4%b8%bb%e5%80%91%e5%bf%83%e4%b8%ad%e7%9a%84top1%e5%93%81%e7%89%8c/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sat, 18 Oct 2025 17:23:54 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[其他]]></category>
