		<title>狗狗不吃飯怎麼辦？從挑食心理 健康警訊 餵食對策全面解析 !</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/17/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e4%b8%8d%e5%90%83%e9%a3%af%e6%80%8e%e9%ba%bc%e8%be%a6%ef%bc%9f%e5%be%9e%e6%8c%91%e9%a3%9f%e5%bf%83%e7%90%86-%e5%81%a5%e5%ba%b7%e8%ad%a6%e8%a8%8a-%e9%a4%b5%e9%a3%9f%e5%b0%8d%e7%ad%96/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 17 Oct 2025 11:27:00 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
